daily_cases_chinacdc_EN: 新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情分布

2019 Novel Coronavirus cumulative cases daily reported by province. Data source is the National Health and provincial health committees, including Hong Kong, Macao and Taiwan. The data are extracted everyday at 16:04 EST. The names of provinces and some columns are translated using Google Translate.
